    <h3> Last Updated: 09-09-2024 </h3> <br />

    Thank you for choosing EduWe, the best training company in the market. This Privacy Policy outlines how EduWe collects, uses, maintains, and discloses information collected from users (each, a "User") of the EduWe website ("Site").
        <br /><br />
    <b>1. Personal Identification Information:</b>
        <br /><br />
